         <abstract id="aspace_9d918873afc639f287879e9fd15c7c80">Julius Kuhnert's drawings, photographs, and one template of designs for buildings in New York City, Rochester, New York and elsewhere. Included is a photograph of wood carvings in the Sterling Memorial Library at Yale University.</abstract>
